{"title":"路","authors":["张志新"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":6,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张志新  遗作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月二十四，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我离开了盘锦大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和那战斗的集体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯朴的贫下中农，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种的高粱苞米。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼没收割，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"营房刚奠基。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎能不怀念它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那哺育我生长的土地！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二月二十五，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我返回了盘锦大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接受批斗的洗礼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做一个“反面”教员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我由衷地感到欣喜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼已收割，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"营房已林立。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎能不感谢他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那锤炼我成长的集体！（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"?  张志新同志生前喜爱的部分书籍"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}